<figureCitation box="[592,725,904,928]" captionStart="Figures 44–47" captionStartId="17.[156,246,1824,1843]" captionTargetBox="[162,766,1061,1771]" captionTargetId="figure-592@17.[376,695,1244,1520]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="Figures 44–47. M. mexicana-subgroup, ovipositors. Fig. 44, dorsal. Figs 45–47, left lateral. 47, right inset, details of ovipositor apex." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5439627" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5439627/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">FIGS 44, 45</figureCitation>
